query:
SELECT 
                routes.id,
                agency_id,
                route_short_name,
                route_long_name,
                route_type,
                route_desc,
                routes.route_code,
                route_paths.route_path
            FROM 
                routes
                LEFT JOIN route_paths on route_paths.route_code = routes.route_code
            WHERE
                route_short_name = $1
                AND routes.city = $2
                AND route_paths.city = $2
